                            <comment id="290240" author="sebastien" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2021 08:50:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;These messages can be harmless. There is a possibility that a client can try to reconnect when the import is being destroyed.  Some outstanding client bound requests are being processed when the imp_sec has already been freed. So we need to ensure to output the error message in import_sec_validate_get() only if the import is not already in the process of being freed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
